Welcome to Podoku 1.0.0!

To play, click "New Game" for a new deck and table then click or drag cards onto the 5x5 play area to form 5-card poker "hands" across every row and column. Each hand will be scored as that row or column is filled.

This game was made in my spare time for fun and to improve my JavaScript knowledge. The HTML/CSS is not polished and planned future improvements include responsiveness, mobile support, and implementation of a true poker quality card shuffling algorithm.
